          "reviewBody": "This is one of the best schools around for Cambridge Curriculum. The management and teachers are carefully chosen and highly qualified, especially when it comes to communication skills. I highly recommend this school for primary classes.\n\nI think this school is undervalued. If promoted properly, it could compete with bigger schools like PeePal and CS Academy. Most of the parents see the cozy buses and the infrastructure, but not the academics and\n\nAreas to improve: Higher Van fees and the playground, offering more emphasis on Hindi and Tamil. Correspondent could be more jovial and she is highly skilled and well trained.",
