            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Rayyan has joined here in his Nestlers. Everyday I pick him up from the school the vibe is different. This school has given us confidence that he would take his studies and discipline to a next level. My sincere thanks to all the staffs, Veena mam and Cameron for all the guidance and support. His HRT and the classroom teacher would send me the weekly planner, his pictures throughout the month, there is a me time scheduled for him at home, bed time routine, wake up routine and what not??? Seeing Rayyan's behavior, positive attitude and communication most of our relatives are checking if they can join their kid here. I would recommend this school to all the kids possible. I am happy that I have found the right place for my son and contended that I have shown him the right direction. This means a lot to us as parents. Wish Rayyan comes out as Cambridge certified. Looking forward. We owe Harvees one!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
